<br>
ears: jasper gold earrings (25pp each) -- 3wis x 2<br>
neck: black iron medallion (25pp) -- 3wis<br>
head: savant's cap (25pp) -- 3wis<br>
face: silver ruby veil (150pp) -- 4wis<br>
fingers: platinum jasper rings (200pp each) -- 6wis x 2<br>
wrists: chipped bone bracelet x 2 (200pp each) -- 5wis x 2<br>
arms: hollowed bone bracers (75pp) -- 15mana<br>
back: kunzar cloak or shimmering white shroud (100pp) -- 2wis or 20mana<br>
chest: foreman's tunic (100pp) -- 3wis<br>
shoulders: lizardscale mantle (50pp) -- 3wis<br>
legs: black chitin leggings (100pp) -- 10mana<br>
feet: vale/mithril/burynai boots (250pp) -- 2wis<br>
primary: velium etched stone mace (300pp) -- 3wis<br>
secondary: charred guardian shield (400pp) -- 9wis -- or do testament of vanear quest for free 10wis secondary item<br>
range: small wisdom deity (200pp) -- 2wis<br>
<br>
Total cost: 2725pp<br>
Total wis: 62 + 25mana<br>
<br>
... leading to a wis of 162-172 or so (1000ish mana at level 30), depending how you allocated your starting points and what race you are.  Most of the above items are pretty common and so you should be able to get them for roughly the prices I listed, depending on your server.  Just look at the wis and cost and the equipment you currently have and figure out what would be the best upgrade for you.... <p><font face="Verdana, Arial" size="2">
